Q1: Role of tester?
Understanding the testing requirements
Planning the tests by defining the strategy
Designing the test cases & preparing the test data
Creating Test Suite.
Executing the test and submitting the status as pass /fail.
Bug Reporting & Coordinating with different departments to fix the bugs
Carry out regression testing every time when changes are made to the code
to fix defects.
In the end, submit the testing report, giving a green signal to the software.

Q2: System Testing?
1. Validating Functional Requirements and Non Functional Requirements of
the System
2. System Testing carried out by the Testers in Customer business point of
view.
3. Customer Business Requirements are inputs to carryout System Testing. 

